Tankor, I concluded your poll because it was obvious that nobody 
was taking it seriously (88 votes... lol), and because it was set to 
finish three years from now. =)

Everyone else, if any of you have polls that have been there for a 
while, it might be a good idea to clean them up a little, there are 
some that have been there for a while. =P

*pulls out his poll broom, and offers it to anyone willing to take it*
